      <title>Markdown</title>
      <link href="/6fc8eab5.html"/>
      <url>/6fc8eab5.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Markdown writing</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="Headings"><a href="#Headings" class="headerlink" title="Headings"></a>Headings</h2><ul><li>#  </li><li>##  </li><li>###  </li><li>####  </li><li>#####   </li><li>######</li></ul><h2 id="Empty-Space"><a href="#Empty-Space" class="headerlink" title="Empty Space"></a>Empty Space</h2><ul><li><strong>&amp;nbsp;</strong> eg. a&nbsp;b  </li><li><strong>&amp;ensp;</strong> eg. a&ensp;b  </li><li><strong>&amp;emsp;</strong> eg. a&emsp;b  </li></ul><h2 id="Quote"><a href="#Quote" class="headerlink" title="Quote"></a>Quote</h2><p>&gt;</p><blockquote><p>abc</p></blockquote><h2 id="Emphasize"><a href="#Emphasize" class="headerlink" title="Emphasize"></a>Emphasize</h2><p>**abc**<br><strong>abc</strong></p><h2 id="Italic"><a href="#Italic" class="headerlink" title="Italic"></a>Italic</h2><p>*abc*<br><em>abc</em></p><h2 id="Delete-Line"><a href="#Delete-Line" class="headerlink" title="Delete Line"></a>Delete Line</h2><p>~~abc~~<br><del>abc</del></p><h2 id="Horizontal-Rule"><a href="#Horizontal-Rule" class="headerlink" title="Horizontal Rule"></a>Horizontal Rule</h2><p>--- or ***</p><hr><h2 id="Paragraphs"><a href="#Paragraphs" class="headerlink" title="Paragraphs"></a>Paragraphs</h2><ul><li>Two empty space at the end of the line;  </li><li>New empty line;</li><li>&lt;br&gt;；</li></ul><h2 id="Tables"><a href="#Tables" class="headerlink" title="Tables"></a>Tables</h2><h3 id="Basic"><a href="#Basic" class="headerlink" title="Basic"></a>Basic</h3><p>|  heading1   | heading2  |<br>|  —-  | —-  |<br>| cell  | cell |<br>| cell  | cell |<br>|  heading1   | heading2  |<br>|  —-  | —-  |<br>| cell  | cell |<br>| cell  | cell<br> |</p><h3 id="Alignment"><a href="#Alignment" class="headerlink" title="Alignment"></a>Alignment</h3><p>-: right<br>:- left<br>:-: middle  </p><h2 id="Lists"><a href="#Lists" class="headerlink" title="Lists"></a>Lists</h2><h3 id="Ordere-Lists"><a href="#Ordere-Lists" class="headerlink" title="Ordere Lists"></a>Ordere Lists</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Markdown</th><th>HTML</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1.<br>2.</td><td>&lt;ol&gt; <br> &nbsp;  &lt;li&gt;First item&lt;/li&gt;  <br>&nbsp;  &lt;li&gt;Second item&lt;/li&gt;  <br>&nbsp;  &lt;li&gt;Third item&lt;/li&gt;  <br>&nbsp;  &lt;li&gt;Fourth item&lt;/li&gt;  <br>&lt;/ol&gt;</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="Unordered-Lists"><a href="#Unordered-Lists" class="headerlink" title="Unordered Lists"></a>Unordered Lists</h3><p>- + * </p><ul><li>abc</li></ul><h2 id="Links"><a href="#Links" class="headerlink" title="Links"></a>Links</h2><ul><li>This is a link. [Baidu](https:/<a href="http://www.baidu.com/">www.baidu.com</a>)</li><li>&lt;<a href="https://www.baidu.com/&gt;">https://www.baidu.com\&gt;</a></li></ul><h2 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h2><ul><li>Use ``<br><code>print(&quot;Hello World&quot;)</code>  </li><li>Use <br>```python <br>&nbsp; print(“Hello World”) <br>```<pre class=" language-python"><code class="language-python"> <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"Hello World"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span></code></pre></li><li>Use &lt;code&gt;nano&lt;/code&gt;<br><code>print("Hello World")</code></li></ul><h2 id="Pictures"><a href="#Pictures" class="headerlink" title="Pictures"></a>Pictures</h2><p>! [ ] ( )</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
