      <title>Hexo+Next 博客升级日志</title>
      <link href="/99263b98.html"/>
      <url>/99263b98.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>前端小菜鸡，到处搬运大佬的博客搭建教程，最后有了自己的博客。把教程都整理了一下。</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="写在前面"><a href="#写在前面" class="headerlink" title="写在前面"></a>写在前面</h1><p>先给自己搭一个，本文讲的是NexT主题配置以及页面的样式优化，参考了许多大佬的文章以及配置文件。在此记录一下做过哪些改动，方便以后自定义，and帮女朋友搭博客。</p><h1 id="基本定义"><a href="#基本定义" class="headerlink" title="基本定义"></a>基本定义</h1><p>在Hexo中自定义主要靠两个文件，./_config.yml(总配置文件) 和 ./themes/next/_.config.yml(主题配置文件)。总配文件匹配的起始目录是source/。<br>在Hexo 8.13.1中，各种自定义文件都放在./source/_data下；各种博文都在./source/_posts下。</p><h1 id="Hexo"><a href="#Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Hexo"></a>Hexo</h1><p>根据官网，安装<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/">hexo</a>。首先是基础软件 nodejs 以及 git，这两个都是常用基础软件所以就不介绍细节了，官网直接安装即可。我们要使用 npm 这个 nodejs 库管理软件。</p><p>由于默认源在国外经常连接超时，所以首先需要修改成国内的镜像源，这里是改成了淘宝的镜像源。</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> config <span class="token keyword">set</span> registry https://registry.npm.taobao.org</code></pre><h2 id="基本命令"><a href="#基本命令" class="headerlink" title="基本命令"></a>基本命令</h2><p><code>hexo init</code>：生成新博客文件夹<br><code>hexo new (page) &quot;xxx&quot;</code>：生成新文章<br><code>hexo clean</code> ：清cache<br><code>hexo generate</code>：生成( <code>hexo g</code> )<br><code>hexo deploy</code>：部署( <code>hexo d</code>)</p><h2 id="安装NexT主题"><a href="#安装NexT主题" class="headerlink" title="安装NexT主题"></a>安装NexT主题</h2><p>hexo有上百种主题，个人使用的是<a href="https://theme-next.js.org/">NexT</a>。安装NexT最新release版本：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">git</span> clone --branch v8.11.1 https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next themes/next</code></pre><p>然后修改总配文件中：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">theme: next</code></pre><h2 id="Hexo配置"><a href="#Hexo配置" class="headerlink" title="Hexo配置"></a>Hexo配置</h2><p>修改总配文件的一些参数，可以参考<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration">官方文档</a>。</p><h3 id="修改博客基本信息"><a href="#修改博客基本信息" class="headerlink" title="修改博客基本信息"></a>修改博客基本信息</h3><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">title: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>博客主题<span class="token operator">></span>subtitle: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>相当于个性签名<span class="token operator">></span>description: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>相当于个性标签<span class="token operator">></span>keywords: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>关键词<span class="token operator">></span>author: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>博主<span class="token operator">></span>language: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>语言（zh-CN）<span class="token operator">></span>timezone: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>时区<span class="token operator">></span></code></pre><h3 id="同步生成文件夹"><a href="#同步生成文件夹" class="headerlink" title="同步生成文件夹"></a>同步生成文件夹</h3><p>将每篇博客对应生成一个文件夹目录（方便插入图片等附件）：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">post_asset_folder: <span class="token boolean">true</span></code></pre><p>md 文件中加入  就可以。</p><h3 id="盘古插件"><a href="#盘古插件" class="headerlink" title="盘古插件"></a>盘古插件</h3><p>在中英文以及数字符合等合适位置，加入空格间隔以美化 UI。在任意位置（最好在#Extensions下）插入：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">pangu: <span class="token boolean">true</span></code></pre><h3 id="部署方式"><a href="#部署方式" class="headerlink" title="部署方式"></a>部署方式</h3><p>设置完此项后，可以用<code>hexo d</code>一键部署。</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">deploy:  type: <span class="token function">git</span>  repo: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>github token<span class="token operator">></span>@<span class="token operator">&lt;</span>仓库git地址<span class="token operator">></span>  branch: master</code></pre><h3 id="搜索功能"><a href="#搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="搜索功能"></a>搜索功能</h3><p>NexT 主题自带了一个搜索功能 Local Search，即在编译文件时本地生成一个数据库，放在网站根目录下，用户借助此数据库进行搜索查询。先安装：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-generator-searchdb --save</code></pre><p>修改总配文件：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">search:  path: search.xml  field: post  format: html  limit: 10000</code></pre><p>修改主配文件：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">local_search:  enable: <span class="token boolean">true</span></code></pre><p>效果：</p><img src="/99263b98/1.png" class=""><h3 id="阅读时间统计"><a href="#阅读时间统计" class="headerlink" title="阅读时间统计"></a>阅读时间统计</h3><p>给博客文章添加一下字数以及阅读时间统计。安装：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-symbols-count-time</code></pre><p>总配文件中加入(awl和wpm参数按照中英混合计算，纯中文为3、200，自行估算)：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">symbols_count_time:  symbols: <span class="token boolean">true</span>  time: <span class="token boolean">true</span>  total_symbols: <span class="token boolean">true</span>  total_time: <span class="token boolean">true</span>  exclude_codeblock: <span class="token boolean">false</span>  awl: 4  wpm: 275  suffix: <span class="token string">"mins."</span></code></pre><h3 id="添加简历"><a href="#添加简历" class="headerlink" title="添加简历"></a>添加简历</h3><p>新建about页面，Markdown中插入PDF。简历PDF制作，可以选择<a href="https://www.wondercv.com/">超级简历</a>。在md文件中：</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>object</span> <span class="token attr-name">height</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>700<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">width</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>950<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">border</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>0<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">data</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>path/my.pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>application/pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>embed</span> <span class="token attr-name">src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>path/my.pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>application/pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">width</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span>800</span> <span class="token attr-name">height</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span>800</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>object</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>或者</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>iframe</span> <span class="token attr-name">src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>/pdf/my.pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token style-attr language-css"><span class="token attr-name"> <span class="token attr-name">style</span></span><span class="token punctuation">="</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token property">width</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">700</span>px<span class="token punctuation">;</span> <span class="token property">height</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token number">950</span>px<span class="token punctuation">;</span></span><span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">frameborder</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>0<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>iframe</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>或者在新窗口打开：</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>object</span> <span class="token attr-name">data</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>http://yoursite.com/the.pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">type</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>application/pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">width</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>700px<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">height</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>700px<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>embed</span> <span class="token attr-name">src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>http://yoursite.com/the.pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>This browser does not support PDFs. Please download the PDF to view it: <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class="token attr-name">href</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>http://yoursite.com/the.pdf<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>Download PDF<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>.<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>embed</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>object</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="不渲染Markdown文件"><a href="#不渲染Markdown文件" class="headerlink" title="不渲染Markdown文件"></a>不渲染Markdown文件</h3><p>在总配文件中，skip_render参数后加入具体文件。添加多个文件如下：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">skip_render: README.md  - <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span>test1/*.html<span class="token variable">`</span></span>  - <span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span>test2/**<span class="token variable">`</span></span></code></pre><h1 id="NexT"><a href="#NexT" class="headerlink" title="NexT"></a>NexT</h1><h2 id="优化"><a href="#优化" class="headerlink" title="优化"></a>优化</h2><h3 id="动态背景"><a href="#动态背景" class="headerlink" title="动态背景"></a>动态背景</h3><p>使背景不那么单调，加入了一个几乎不影响性能的背景动画。 在 source/_data 目录 (若不存在则新建一个) 下新建文件 footer.njk，内容：</p><pre class=" language-html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class="token attr-name">color</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>0,0,255<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">opacity</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>0.5<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">zIndex</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>-1<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">count</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>99<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span> <span class="token attr-name">src</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>https://lib.baomitu.com/canvas-nest.js/1.0.1/canvas-nest.js<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span class="token script language-javascript"></span><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre><p>可以修改数量，透明度，颜色。<br>在主配文件中找到 custom_file_path 一项将 footer 一行取消注释：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">custom_file_path:  footer: source/_data/footer.njk</code></pre><h3 id="设置阅读进度"><a href="#设置阅读进度" class="headerlink" title="设置阅读进度"></a>设置阅读进度</h3><p>安装moon-cake。</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-cake-moon-menu</code></pre><p>主配文件新增：</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">moon_menu<span class="token punctuation">:</span>  back2top<span class="token punctuation">:</span>    enable<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span>    icon<span class="token punctuation">:</span> fas fa<span class="token operator">-</span>chevron<span class="token operator">-</span>up    order<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">1</span>  back2bottom<span class="token punctuation">:</span>    enable<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token boolean">true</span>    icon<span class="token punctuation">:</span> fas fa<span class="token operator">-</span>chevron<span class="token operator">-</span>down    order<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token operator">-</span><span class="token number">2</span></code></pre><p>效果：</p><img src="/99263b98/2.png" class=""><h3 id="加载进度条"><a href="#加载进度条" class="headerlink" title="加载进度条"></a>加载进度条</h3><p>主配文件中pace下设置为true，选择样式。需要用npm提前安装对应的依赖。</p><h3 id="摘要"><a href="#摘要" class="headerlink" title="摘要"></a>摘要</h3><p>在每篇博客中加入&lt;!–more–&gt;，之前的内容则会作为摘要。</p><h3 id="粒子钟"><a href="#粒子钟" class="headerlink" title="粒子钟"></a>粒子钟</h3><h4 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h4><p>在\source_data目录下，新建sidebar.njk文件，并在主配文件中custom_file_path添加。内容如<a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/1934193">链接</a>。</p><h4 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h4><p>在主配文件custome_file_path下添加：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">custom_file_path:  sidebar: source/_data/sidebar.njk</code></pre><h3 id="设置背景"><a href="#设置背景" class="headerlink" title="设置背景"></a>设置背景</h3><p>在source/_data文件夹下，新建styles.styl，并取消主配文件中的注释。</p><pre class=" language-styl"><code class="language-styl">body &#123;    background-image: url(“xxx”);     background-repeat: no-repeat;    background-attachment: fixed;    background-size: 100% 100%;&#125;</code></pre><h3 id="右上角fork"><a href="#右上角fork" class="headerlink" title="右上角fork"></a>右上角fork</h3><p>选择样式。<a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https://github.com/blog/273-github-ribbons">链接</a>。</p><p>复制。将地址更改为自己主页。</p><p>打开next/layout/_layout.njk，把代码复制到<code>&lt;div class=&quot;headband&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</code>下面。</p><h3 id="设置主页博客块状"><a href="#设置主页博客块状" class="headerlink" title="设置主页博客块状"></a>设置主页博客块状</h3><p>在source/_data文件夹下，新建styles.styl，并取消主配文件中的注释。</p><pre class=" language-styl"><code class="language-styl">.main-inner &#123;    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);    padding: 0px 40px 40px 40px;&#125;.post-block&#123;        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);        //margin-top: 24px;        margin-bottom: 24px;        padding: 20px;        border-radius: 30px 30px 30px 30px;        box-shadow: 8px 7px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.12), 7px 4px 1px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.06), 0 1px 5px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.12);&#125;.post &#123;   margin-top: 60px;   padding: 5px;   margin-bottom: 60px;   -webkit-box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(120, 128, 114, 1.5);   -moz-box-shadow: 0 0 5px rgba(202, 203, 204, .5);&#125;</code></pre><h3 id="设置所有边框为圆角"><a href="#设置所有边框为圆角" class="headerlink" title="设置所有边框为圆角"></a>设置所有边框为圆角</h3><p>在source/_data文件夹下，新建variables.styl，并取消主配文件中的注释。</p><pre class=" language-styl"><code class="language-styl">$border-radius-inner     = 20px 20px 20px 20px;$border-radius           = 20px;</code></pre><h3 id="设置头像"><a href="#设置头像" class="headerlink" title="设置头像"></a>设置头像</h3><p>主配文件中搜索avatar，修改url。</p><h3 id="设置社交链接"><a href="#设置社交链接" class="headerlink" title="设置社交链接"></a>设置社交链接</h3><p>主配文件中Social中取消注释，添加链接，添加图标。</p><h3 id="设置友链"><a href="#设置友链" class="headerlink" title="设置友链"></a>设置友链</h3><p>主配文件中Blog rolls中在links添加。</p><h2 id="新增功能"><a href="#新增功能" class="headerlink" title="新增功能"></a>新增功能</h2><h3 id="添加评论系统"><a href="#添加评论系统" class="headerlink" title="添加评论系统"></a>添加评论系统</h3><p>本博客使用的是 <strong>Waline</strong> 评论系统，是基于 <strong>LeanCloud</strong> 存储的系统。使用的是最简单、零成本的部署方式。</p><p>Step1. 注册客户端。注册一个<a href="https://console.leancloud.app/register">LeanCloud国际版</a>账号。国内版需要备案的域名，国际版有公用的。如果显示国际版不支持中国大陆，请忽略它。</p><p>Step2. 注册完成后，登录，然后找到<strong>创建应用</strong>。填写你的应用名称,名称可以自己定义，然后，下面选择开发版 点击创建。点击应用进入设置。</p><p>Step3. 点击应用凭证，取得我们 AppKey 、App id 、以及 MasterKey。</p><p>Step4. 安装服务端。Waline 支持多种服务端，为了最简便上手，我们使用在 Vercl 上安装服务端。首先，点击 <a href="https://vercel.com/import/project?template=https://github.com/walinejs/waline/tree/main/example">一键部署</a>。需要注册一个账号，支持使用 Github 账号直接登录。登录后重新点进来，点击 Create。输入好点击Create后，等待下面 Deploy 构建完成，点击 Go to Dashboard。</p><p>Step5. 找到 Settings =&gt; Environment Variables，配置环境变量。三个环境变量对应先前的应用凭证：</p><table><thead><tr><th align="center">LeanCloud</th><th align="center">Vercel Environment</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">AppID</td><td align="center">LEAN_ID</td></tr><tr><td align="center">AppKey</td><td align="center">LEAN_KEY</td></tr><tr><td align="center">MasterKey</td><td align="center">LEAN_MASTER_KEY</td></tr></tbody></table><ul><li>如果你使用 LeanCloud 国内版，请额外配置 LEAN_SERVER 环境变量，值为你绑定好的域名。</li></ul><p>Step6. 为了使环境变量生效，需要重新构建一次。在上方找到 Deployments ，选择第一个右边的三个点，点击 Redeploy 。等待其构建结束，然后记住 DOMAINS 中的域名地址。</p><p>Step7. 配置。安装：</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> @waline/hexo-next</code></pre><p>在主配中加入</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Waline</span><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># For more information: https://waline.js.org, https://github.com/walinejs/waline</span>waline:  enable: <span class="token boolean">true</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">#是否开启</span>  serverURL: waline-server-pearl.vercel.app <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Waline #服务端地址，我们这里就是上面部署的 Vercel 地址</span>  placeholder: 请文明评论呀 <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># #评论框的默认文字</span>  avatar: mm <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 头像风格</span>  meta: <span class="token punctuation">[</span>nick, mail, link<span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 自定义评论框上面的三个输入框的内容</span>  pageSize: 10 <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 评论数量多少时显示分页</span>  lang: zh-cn <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 语言, 可选值: en, zh-cn</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Warning: 不要同时启用 `waline.visitor` 以及 `leancloud_visitors`.</span>  visitor: <span class="token boolean">false</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 文章阅读统计</span>  comment_count: <span class="token boolean">true</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 如果为 false , 评论数量只会在当前评论页面显示, 主页则不显示</span>  requiredFields: <span class="token punctuation">[</span><span class="token punctuation">]</span> <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># 设置用户评论时必填的信息，[nick,mail]: [nick] | [nick, mail]</span>  libUrl: <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true"># Set custom library cdn url</span></code></pre><h3 id="添加在线聊天系统"><a href="#添加在线聊天系统" class="headerlink" title="添加在线聊天系统"></a>添加在线聊天系统</h3><p>NexT支持几种在线聊天系统，本博客选用的是TiDio。</p><p>Step1. 注册<a href="https://www.tidio.com/">Tidio账号</a>。</p><p>Step2. 点击后台，点击设置，点击Developer。将Public Key复制到主配文件中。</p><pre class=" language-bash"><code class="language-bash">tidio:  enable: <span class="token boolean">true</span>  key: <span class="token operator">&lt;</span>public key<span class="token operator">></span> </code></pre><h4 id="登陆服务端"><a href="#登陆服务端" class="headerlink" title="登陆服务端"></a>登陆服务端</h4><p>Waline 有服务端，支持评论管理。我们需要注册一个账号作为管理员。<a href="waline.alexhan.life/ui">服务端</a>。</p><p>找到评论框，点击 登录 按钮，会弹出一个窗口，找到用户注册，默认第一个注册的用户为管理员，所以部署好一定要记得及时注册。</p><p>注册好，登录之后即可进入评论管理的后台，可以对评论进行管理。</p><h1 id="部署在Github"><a href="#部署在Github" class="headerlink" title="部署在Github"></a>部署在Github</h1><ul><li>优点：免费薅羊毛，不限流量，支持静态脚本</li><li>缺点：国内访问不稳定，图片可能加载不出来</li><li>对Github不熟悉的朋友，可以参考博客下的Github教程。</li></ul><p>Step1. 新建一个项目（项目名设置成：&lt;github username&gt; +github.io）(只能建一个)</p><p>Step2. </p>]]></content>
      
      
      
